<i>adjective</i>: 피로하다 [피로하다], 피곤하다 [피곤하다], 곤핍하다 [곤ː피파다] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>adjective</i><br>
<dt>피로하다 [피로하다]</dt><br>
<dd>tired; exhausted; fatigued</dd><br>
<dd>몸이나 정신이 지쳐서 힘들다.</dd><br>
<dd>Being tired and worn-out physically or mentally.</dd><br>
<dt>피곤하다 [피곤하다]</dt><br>
<dd>tired; exhausted; fatigued</dd><br>
<dd>몸이나 마음이 지쳐서 힘들다.</dd><br>
<dd>Being tired and worn-out physically or mentally.</dd><br>
<dt>곤핍하다 [곤ː피파다]</dt><br>
<dd>fatigued; tired; weary</dd><br>
<dd>몹시 지치고 고단하다.</dd><br>
<dd>Very exhausted and tired.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>